OL,5, Digital sales accounted for almost nine
OL,6, out of every 10 video games sold in the
OL,7, UK in 2022, according to a trade body. 
OL,9,FThe digital entertainment and retail   
OL,10,Fassociation (ERA) said 89.5% of games  
OL,11,Fsold had been digital downloads and the
OL,12,Fremaining 10.5% actual physical copies.
OL,14,FAbout 30% of the sales came from mobile
OL,15,Fapps, which are sold digitally.        
OL,17,FIn total, the gaming industry accounted
OL,18,Ffor #4.7bn of sales in the UK in 2022 -
OL,19,Fhigher than that of the film,          
OL,20,Ftelevision or music industries.        
